7KdcBGgAZ/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国海军称伊朗布雷旨在引导船只靠近其海岸"&gt;发挥自己的优势&lt;/a&gt;，实施霍尔木兹海峡采矿战略，似乎旨在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Lq7a3wflOmEgyVw4ycR8PAs6JGJiUuzqd6K40I-3y321AERA5TSgTZueHnowkoKXv8pco1338-M7i0gvGXbDUHVRpOXNKJlcNCFt0YxihjIhbpraR0XXPkfmqRtvENP_K0AxSF_y8g_u3lozIQ_fDlkNTiAs8JsSpg6nqQbMi3LpMwoeoCsMJQRDt1L2hl1Jfd_shw5bfg_nJ3ypTtYF427BiUvjSbzdXwzySvZaDO5fnTfj5CB6GODSJgptdDAjAZFU8wQ6KxAjfg4P9XS1vp4BuQk2QWqMwoiOkXqq027h3WxBNMcIZVHsbtaH4OmrkzZeL-HxJMmSfixOdQ7pUarcl1Og3q7_J4o5uLzfr9IPe26WRwiZqzyV638AAJWsklTkouie2Fcw53RKxabr8l6AQ_igI12FiIfxZ7wD_0XrhVp9sfmdJAXM8UHVPROenuePI_h_fwIn1ZXVLcZANDad1Q9JZtJRuqfi8nKB3slqXvYjYI5IUOIT280DKCREYyLjRfHUvQbPaXXZwnFl_RruyQ/JRdz4LP4aH9EJGH0X0-w7JNW7HYd5nvO/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗告诉联合国它有权控制霍尔木兹海峡的“部分”"&gt;引导其海岸附近的商业航运&lt;/a&gt;。如果美国关于采矿的说法属实，那么德黑兰将更容易控制交通和收取通行费——而在美国和以色列发动战争之前，德黑兰并没有获得这些好处。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;自从双方同意根据上个月的协议重新开放霍尔木兹海峡以来，穿过霍尔木兹的路线一直是一个关键的热点。伊朗表示，未经其许可，船只不得通过，而美国则试图引导海峡沿阿曼一侧的航运。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/USZR3wQOgwy1Q21nX_9CIr-8tyq_0-uaU8AEAVZsMaDvcKr_uT3oD8legzQXREivGZAPIgbc6xDA1uMNBz_grzv1GgKczn5CTMZ-qknzfeI5VHrPwzRsNyGDqHgzhd3SZh7LQiV8WvddATmBAkdDMTTIRHutPJJtInRe9XyllvPPM0XTz1O3DenRobLqupUljU0ZJ7xrIA-njZsOpbOFveIgfAGGbELPzQsjoPU62vdFD3R-k_vL8KyhtRAsaSA5BLIs1Mz-S3bCiqgOzpFV2OanVMZ67iY_K8m0FOSoOOzQb_lwCXd0Bv5MValRB-G-W-mFPisoLkUc77pwhvLUqP8OwmwBTSAVu6ZaeuUTfMeqn9j1IB9OPTyCC4Qr5DtkeigifsHiKD-PwJqpkt6pJ1h0UZdErChX2MZ1E8lwOmijguyFePhpSi1K9wT7TCvTMakjy7opaTY-uN19PC9SVUg691dor1uz15LSmldLcLMe1kwsWfX1jP5GLrHw88a0foI7-s9k6Sw1vmyvmm2MsEPSEwzK/GGMimpA7WFyBcB5wA8diV1z2Odrq-TVF/22" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjW